          Hello, my name is
        </h1>
        <h2 class="text-darkSecondaryText z-10 text-7xl font-semibold">
          Bret Gomes
        </h2>
        <h3 class="text-darkPrimaryText text-7xl font-semibold mt-1">
          Full Stack Developer
        </h3>
        <p class="text-darkSecondaryText text-lg mt-5">
          My focus is on developing user-centric web applications with an
          emphasis on mobile responsiveness. Driven by a passion for solving
          practical problems through code, I aim to create solutions that
          enhance everyday life. I'm currently seeking a collaborative team
          environment where innovative ideas and a dedication to quality are
          deeply valued.
        </p>
      </section>
