        <ul>
          <li>
            <img
              src="/Typescript_logo_2020.svg"
              alt="TypeScript Logo"
              style="height: 24px;"
            />

            <strong>TypeScript & JavaScript:</strong> For robust and dynamic
            applications.
          </li>
          <li>
            <img src="React-icon.svg" alt="React Logo" style="height: 24px;" />
            <strong>React:</strong> Crafting interactive user interfaces.
          </li>
