              src="/Node.js_logo.svg"
              alt="Node JS Logo"
              style="height: 24px;"
            />
            <strong>Node.js:</strong> Building efficient back-end services.
          </li>
          <li>
            <img
              src="/Tailwind_CSS_Logo.svg"
              alt="Tailwind CSS Logo"
              style="height: 24px;"
            />
            <strong>Tailwind:</strong> Designing stylish and responsive layouts.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          I'm currently focused on enhancing my full-stack development skills
          and am keen to explore Rust in the future, attracted by its static
